'''CBS體育網'''（CBS Sports Network）是[[美國|美國]]的一個[[有線電視|有線電視]]和[[衛星電視|衛星電視]]頻道，由[[CBS集團|CBS集團]]所有。CBS體育網開始播出於2002年，當時的名稱是全國校園體育網（'''National College Sports Network'''，後改為'''CSTV'''），主要轉播大學體育賽事。2005年，CSTV被CBS收購<ref>{{cite news | first = David | last = Whitford | title = The king of the sports deal | date = 2010-05-25 | url = http://money.cnn.com/2010/05/10/news/companies/greenberg_sports_deal_king.fortune/ | work = [[Fortune_(magazine)|Fortune]] | accessdate = 2010-06-02 | archive-date = 2010-05-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100522034442/http://money.cnn.com/2010/05/10/news/companies/greenberg_sports_deal_king.fortune/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>，改名為CBS校園體育網（CBS College Sports Network）。2011年，該頻道再改名為CBS體育網<ref>{{cite web |url=http://fangsbites.com/2011/02/cbs-college-sports-rebrands-as-cbs-sports-network/ |title=CBS College Sports Rebrands As CBS Sports Network |author= |date=February 15, 2011 |work= |publisher=Fang's Bites |accessdate=15 February 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110710223844/http://fangsbites.com/2011/02/cbs-college-sports-rebrands-as-cbs-sports-network/ |archivedate=2011年7月10日 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://fangsbites.com/2011/04/cbs-college-sports-rebrands-after-ncaa-championship-game/ | title=CBS College Sports Rebrands After NCAA Championship Game | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110407144759/http://fangsbites.com/2011/04/cbs-college-sports-rebrands-after-ncaa-championship-game | archivedate=2011-04-07 | accessdate=2016-02-27 }}</ref>。

